    {
      "instruction": "<p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces and grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced ciabatta</strong> to a separate baking tray and spread one side with <strong>butter</strong> and your<strong> cranberry sauce</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>torn mozzarella</strong> and <strong>grated cheese </strong>and set aside for later</p>",
