    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>parsnip soup</strong> in bowls with the<strong> cheesy cranberry toasties</strong> to the side for dipping</p><p>Garnish the soup with the<strong> apple matchsticks</strong>, <strong>reserved thyme leaves</strong>, a grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
